---
import ContentLayout from '../layouts/ContentLayout.astro';
---

<ContentLayout title="About Us">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg">
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
                Alpha Gamma Omega is the largest college social fraternity in the world with more than 200,000 living members, including over 17,000 undergraduates and more than 300 chapters and colonies located throughout the United States and Canada. Founded in 1869 at the University of Virginia, Alpha Gamma Omega International Headquarters is based in Charlottesville, Virginia.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Our Purposes as a Fraternity</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
                Believing in the Lord Jesus Christ as our personal Savior, we, as Christian young men of Alpha Gamma Omega Fraternity purpose that it shall be the aim of this fraternity:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-8">
                <li>To win others to a saving knowledge of Jesus Christ,</li>
                <li>To promote Christian fellowship,</li>
                <li>To present Christian ideals in word and deed,</li>
                <li>To search reverently for the truth,</li>
                <li>To uphold the traditions and ideals of the university,</li>
                <li>And to deepen the spiritual lives of the members.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
                To provide a Christ-centered brotherhood that enhances the college experience and develops men of God who will be influential leaders in their communities, churches, and families.
            </p>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12">
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Brotherhood</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                        We foster genuine relationships built on Christian principles, mutual respect, and shared experiences that last a lifetime.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Faith</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                        Our foundation is built on Christian values, encouraging spiritual growth and development among our members.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Leadership</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                        We develop tomorrow's leaders through hands-on experience, mentorship, and character development.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Service</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                        We are committed to serving our community, both on campus and beyond, making a positive impact wherever we go.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</ContentLayout> 